intltool: intltool (International Translations Tool)
intltool:
intltool: The intltool package is used to:
intltool:
intltool: * Extract translatable strings from various source files.
intltool: * Collect the extracted strings together with messages from traditional
intltool:   source files.
intltool: * Merge back the translations from .po files into .xml, .desktop and
intltool:   .oaf files.
